{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "my-verse-api-collection",
    "name": "My Verse API",
    "description": "My Verse backend API (Phase 1 + Phase 2).\n\nBase URL: {{baseUrl}}\n\n**Registration flow:**\n1. Run **Media → Upload Profile Image** → sets `profilePictureMeta`\n2. Run **Auth → Register** with `profilePicture` from that meta object\n\n**Project flow:**\n1. **Auth → Login (Admin)**\n2. **Projects → Create Book** → sets `projectId`\n3. **Sections → Create Section** → sets `sectionId`\n4. **Section Items → Add Text Item**\n5. **Sections → Publish Section** then **Projects → Publish Project**\n\nImport **My Verse — Local** environment.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{accessToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "staffProfileId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "profilePictureMeta",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "projectId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "sectionId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "sectionItemId",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "projectImageMeta",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "projectVideoMeta",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Public. Returns app and MongoDB connection status."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (Public)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"username\": \"johndoe\",\n  \"password\": \"securePass123\",\n  \"displayName\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"profilePicture\": {{profilePictureMeta}}\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Public. Creates a PUBLIC user. Run Media → Upload Profile Image first (optional profilePicture)."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201 || pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  }",
                  "  if (json.data && json.data.user && json.data.user.id) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userId', json.data.user.id);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', json.data.user.id);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Register (Staff)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"performer@example.com\",\n  \"username\": \"star_performer\",\n  \"password\": \"securePass123\",\n  \"displayName\": \"Star Performer\",\n  \"profilePicture\": {{profilePictureMeta}},\n  \"stageName\": \"Star\",\n  \"bio\": \"Professional performer\",\n  \"location\": \"Los Angeles\",\n  \"skills\": [\"acting\", \"voice\"]\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register/staff",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register", "staff"]
            },
            "description": "Public. JSON body with required profilePicture FileMeta. Run Media → Upload Profile Image first."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201 || pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "  }",
                  "  if (json.data && json.data.user) {",
                  "    pm.environment.set('userId', json.data.user.id);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', json.data.user.id);",
                  "    if (json.data.user.staffProfile && json.data.user.staffProfile.id) {",
                  "      pm.environment.set('staffProfileId', json.data.user.staffProfile.id);",
                  "      pm.collectionVariables.set('staffProfileId', json.data.user.staffProfile.id);",
                  "    }",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": []
        },
